text: Good food, the price was reasonable for some food from Collins. The texture of surface the onion rings were smooth unlike most other stores which made it really nice to eat without all the breadcrumbs you'd usually get from them.
Tried the new Common Grill outlet at Jelita Shopping Centre, and it did not disappoint! The food quality is top-notch, with generous portions and well-executed flavors at very affordable prices.
